    "our_mission_description": [
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Places are the perfect gateways to inspire and connect people. Our mission is to inspire and create unique, warm environments where people can come together. \n\nAs you step into our resort, you will immediately notice the creative blend of the local environment with modern design, which has served as a great source of inspiration for us. We believe that spaces are not just physical, but also have the power to generate emotional experiences that can last a lifetime.",
